<p corresp='TTP32056024P1' xml:id='OTP32056024P1'>28 or 30 years old 5 ft 6 or 7 in high. Weighs about 135 <add place='above'>lbs</add>.
</p>

<p corresp='TTP32056024P2' xml:id='OTP32056024P2'>Fair complection, Dark Brown hair dark Sandy Beard, rather hasty Small Squint Yellow or hazle eyes a little Scrofulous a little drooped in the <hi rend='underline'>shoulders</hi>, Bad count-nance
</p>

<p corresp='TTP32056024P3' xml:id='OTP32056024P3'><rs ref='#S32021816'>H Clay Smith</rs>
</p>

<p corresp='TTP32056024P4' xml:id='OTP32056024P4'>21 years old 5 ft 8 or 9 in high well made weighs about 155 or 60 <add place='above'>lbs</add> fair complec-tion. dark sandy hair Beard light, His eyes probable hazle slightly scrofulous
</p>

<p corresp='TTP32056024P5' xml:id='OTP32056024P5'><rs ref='#S32021817'>Nick Christian</rs>
</p>

<p corresp='TTP32056024P6' xml:id='OTP32056024P6'>About 21 years old 5 ft 5 or 6 in high maybe about 130 <add place='above'>lbs</add> Very dark com-lexion Black hair very little Beard with Black mustach, Blue eyes and large nose.
</p>


